snippet.title: HGPTV (Channel16 Cable67)
snippet.description:
HGPTV Channel 16/Cable67 is "THE  NEWS  AND ENTERTAINMENT CHANNEL".  Our company focus is to produce outstanding Quality, Educational and Entertaining products and also to broadcast a mixture of local and foreign content. Our initiatives is to generate fresh ideas and concepts to enhance creativity, maintain freshness to ensure the longevity of our station. HGPTV - "THE  NEWS AND ENTERTAINMENT CHANNEL", currently has a geographical broadcast footprint in Regions 3, 4, 5, 6 and 7, attracting a growing captive audience on the East Coast of Region 4. 
HGPTV will continue to invest and support our local communities by airing programs like our HGP Community Magazine, started in 2012, and delve deeply in order to showcase unique features and customs, of how the people of individual villages live their lives.

HGPTV Omar Farouk (HGPTV Channel 16/67)
1 Republic Drive, Beterverwagting, East Coast Demerara, Guyana
Main Reception: 592-220-3660
E-Mail: channel16.67@hgptv.com
